title: 820-3476 Green Light, fan spins and immediately shuts down
message: Check for corrosion around SPI, measure all traces and resistors on SPI lines.....

title: 820-3476 Green Light, fan spins and immediately shuts down
message: WORKING!! Looked for corrosion around SPI, none, but found some around U5110! Replaced U5110 and ran a trace from pin 1 to C5120 and working!  Thank you aprendiz for your prompt reply and help.  Much appreciated!!

title: 820-3476 Green Light, fan spins and immediately shuts down
message: U5110 can only cause a completely dead machine. Something else that was heated up was the issue, so the problem may return. Corrosion under J6100 is common.
